casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
GUTIERREZ S252532 Supreme Court of California. JANUARY 2, 2019 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of related issues in People v. Arredondo, S233582 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court. The request for an order directing depublication of the opinion in the above-entitled appeal is denied.
